    shell of /bin/false was preventing it from starting under sysvinit. Thanks to
    Michal Humpula <michal.humpula@hudrydum.cz>. (Closes: #798951)

 -- Chris Lamb <lamby@debian.org>  Mon, 14 Sep 2015 14:13:26 +0100

