    - ./utils/lru/
    - ./src/redis-trib.rb
    - Don't compress redis-trib.rb
    - Add ruby-redis to Suggests.

 -- Chris Lamb <lamby@debian.org>  Sat, 11 Jul 2015 15:23:33 +0100

redis (2:3.0.2-2) unstable; urgency=medium

